phpMyFirewall


open up setup.php and change the path
to your php binary installation
default is #!/usr/bin/php -q
possible examples: 
#!/usr/local/php/bin/php -q
or
#!/usr/local/bin/php -q


then run chmod 755 setup.php
and execute 
./setup.php --check
if all pass's the system sanity checks proceed 

open up etc/config.php and edit accordingly